</P>
<P>
Karachi: min. 27 degrees c., max. 34 degrees c., cloudy, calm
to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Cairo: min. 21 degrees c., max. 34 degrees c., clear, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Moscow: min. 4 degrees c., max. 13 degrees c., cloudy to
drizzle, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Frankfurt: min. 10 degrees c., max. 18 degrees c., overcast,
calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Paris: min. 10 degrees c., max. 16 degrees c., overcast, calm
to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
London: min. 8 degrees c., max. 14 degrees c., clear, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
New York: min. 11 degrees c., max. 20 degrees c., clear, calm
to gentle breeze. 
</P>
</TEXT>
