<HEADLINE> Yeltsin to Sack Defense Minister </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, May 22 (Xinhua) -- Russian President Boris Yeltsin has
decided to dismiss Defense Minister Igor Rodionov for his failure
to reform Russia's armed forces, Itar-Tass news agency reported
today. 
</P>
</TEXT>
