dispute over an outstanding debt amounting to 600,000 U.S.
Dollars which the state-owned Sizarail of Zaire owes to Zambia
Railways.
</P>
<P>
The new Zairean authorities reportedly proposed to swap debts
as Zambia Railways also owes a firm in Zaire 755,000 Dollars.
