attention to women's soccer. "We never expect they will cover the
sport in an all-round way, but they should have more report on
it. Some newspapers even report nothing about the results of our
first division league," she said.
</P>
<P>
Beckenbauer also advised the media, especially TV stations,
give more attention to women's soccer.
</P>
<P>
Wiegmann was the second footballer to win the award following
Martina Voss. 
